2003-03-11 Andreas Pohl <osar@users.sourceforge.net>
	* Release of perlrapi 0.2:
	  * Rapi2::Defs v0.02:
	    - Added defines from rapi_types.h
	    - Documentation, you can visit all defines now by using `perldoc Rapi2::Defs'
	  * Rapi2 v0.02:
	    - New functions:
	        CeRegOpenKeyEx, CeRegCloseKey, CeRegCreateKeyEx, CeRegQueryInfoKey,
	        CeRegQueryValueEx, CeRegSetValueEx, CeRegEnumValue (returns the names
	        only, see the comments for details), CeRegEnumKeyEx (returns the names
	        only)
	  * Rapi2::Simple v0.03:
	    - Implemented registry access methods:
	      OpenKey, OpenSubKey, CloseKey, GetSubKeyNames, GetValueNames, KeyValue,
	      GetInfoKey
	
2003-03-06 Andreas Pohl <osar@users.sourceforge.net>
	* Rapi2::Simple:
	  - Fixed OpenDB(): when opened by OID, the obejct type was not set
	* Rapi2:
	  - CEVALUNION: 'USHORT uiVal' to 'WORD uiVal'
	                'ULONG ulVal' to 'DWORD ulVal'
	    (to avoid mapping to pointers)
	* Sample/dump.pl:
	  - Stores a Database dump to an XML file.

2003-03-05 Andreas Pohl <osar@users.sourceforge.net>
	* Sample/ls.pl:
	  - The pls implementation in Perl.
	* Rapi2::Simple 0.02.1:
	  - FLAGS argument for FileList(), to overwrite the default combination

2003-03-04 Andreas Pohl <osar@users.sourceforge.net>
	* Rapi2 0.01.1:
	  - Fixed CeGetSpecialFolderPath typemap in the SWIG interface
	  - Documentation
	* Rapi2::Simple 0.02:
	  - New methods: 
	      store, DBList, OpenFile, CloseFile, ReadFile, WriteFile, CopyFile,
	      MoveFile, DeleteFile, DeleteDir, FileList, FileAttr, GetSpecialFolderPath
	  - Documentation
	  - Changed return value of fetch()
	    (the hash contains now array references, to store the type of properties)
	    -> Sample/ldif_imp.pl (uses fetch(), so it had to be changed)
	* Sample/ldif_imp.pl:
	  - Fixed import of CE_ADD_COUNTRY
	
2003-02-25 Andreas Pohl <osar@users.sourceforge.net>
	* Initial Release of perlrapi 0.1

